rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-navy\">Format</p><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Online veya yüz yüze</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-border/80 bg-ivory/65 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wallet-cards mt-1 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2\"></path><path d=\"M3 11h3c.8 0 1.6.3 2.1.9l1.1.9c1.6 1.6 4.1 1.6 5.7 0l1.1-.9c.5-.5 1.3-.9 2.1-.9H21\"></path></svg><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-navy\">Ücret</p><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground\">Atölye tarihine göre değişir</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container grid gap-10 pb-14 sm:pb-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.82fr_1.18fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Program</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Bu eğitimde neler var?</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Kendi haritası üzerinde çalışarak öğrenmek isteyen, deneyim odaklı katılımcılar.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex gap-4 p-5 sm:gap-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy text-sm text-primary-foreground\">1</span><div><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Kısa numeroloji temeli</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Modül, canlı anlatım ve örneklerle desteklenen uygulamalı bir akış içinde işlenir.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex gap-4 p-5 sm:gap-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy text-sm text-primary-foreground\">2</span><div><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Kişisel harita çalışma sayfası</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Modül, canlı anlatım ve örneklerle desteklenen uygulamalı bir akış içinde işlenir.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex gap-4 p-5 sm:gap-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy text-sm text-primary-foreground\">3</span><div><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Grup içinde örnek okumalar</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Modül, canlı anlatım ve örneklerle desteklenen uygulamalı bir akış içinde işlenir.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex gap-4 p-5 sm:gap-5 sm:p-6\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-navy text-sm text-primary-foreground\">4</span><div><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Kapanış niyeti ve uygulama planı</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Modül, canlı anlatım ve örneklerle desteklenen uygulamalı bir akış içinde işlenir.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white/34 py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"container grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><h2 class=\"font-editorial text-3xl text-navy\">Katılımcılar ne öğrenir?</h2><ul class=\"mt-5 grid gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Kendi temel sayılarını yorumlama</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Güçlü ve geliştirilmesi gereken alanları fark etme</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Kişisel yıl temasını okuma</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Günlük yaşama aktarım önerileri</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><h2 class=\"font-editorial text-3xl text-navy\">Eğitim sonunda</h2><ul class=\"mt-5 grid gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Haritanı daha anlaşılır bir çerçevede görürsün.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Sayıların sende hangi temalara işaret ettiğini keşfedersin.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-sm leading-7\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>Kişisel gelişim yolculuğuna pratik bir farkındalık alanı eklersin.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container grid gap-10 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">SSS</span><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-[1.1] text-navy sm:text-5xl sm:leading-[1.08]\">Eğitim hakkında merak edilenler.</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\">Program detayları dönemsel duyuruya göre netleşebilir.</p></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur\"><div class=\"min-w-0 sm:p-6 sm:pt-0 p-6\"><div class=\"w-full\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"border-b border-border/80\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_5kav5ubtb_\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_1kav5ubtb_\" class=\"flex flex-1 items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left text-base font-medium text-navy transition-all hover:text-gold [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180\" data-radix-collection-item=\"\">Atölye kişisel bilgileri içeriyor mu?<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_5kav5ubtb_\" hidden=\"\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"radix-_R_1kav5ubtb_\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"overflow-hidden text-sm text-muted-foreground data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down\" style=\"--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)\"></div></div><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"border-b border-border/80\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" dat